  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/63e33cb88b8c6369ac687525441c0d03.poster.avif?t=1752489081\" width=500 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/63e33cb88b8c6369ac687525441c0d03.webm?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/63e33cb88b8c6369ac687525441c0d03.mp4?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has their own strengths, cultivate the character you like, make them invincible and invincible! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also characters from other factions waiting for your recruitment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/7da2ed5bd3bce980b68494b8ec11e0b0.poster.avif?t=1752489081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/7da2ed5bd3bce980b68494b8ec11e0b0.webm?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/7da2ed5bd3bce980b68494b8ec11e0b0.mp4?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/b3cf1e189be9367dce2e8c6be98e1b3f.poster.avif?t=1752489081\" width=500 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/b3cf1e189be9367dce2e8c6be98e1b3f.webm?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/b3cf1e189be9367dce2e8c6be98e1b3f.mp4?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose equipment that better suits the character, making it invincible and invincible. Paired with personality and skills, it will take you to experience the pleasure of mowing grass in battle chess games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/bc3040dedd7dff5dc089f596af0c37fe.poster.avif?t=1752489081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/bc3040dedd7dff5dc089f596af0c37fe.webm?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/bc3040dedd7dff5dc089f596af0c37fe.mp4?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/884f278da8dd9a899fddce9cfcf340c9.poster.avif?t=1752489081\" width=500 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/884f278da8dd9a899fddce9cfcf340c9.webm?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/884f278da8dd9a899fddce9cfcf340c9.mp4?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By achieving the hidden conditions in the levels, you will be able to change history and alter the character's ending!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/95ea0cc313bce299245cc33a60c5e6f2.poster.avif?t=1752489081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/95ea0cc313bce299245cc33a60c5e6f2.webm?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910960/extras/95ea0cc313bce299245cc33a60c5e6f2.mp4?t=1752489081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
